    {
      "text": "<p>Ako postoji fajl pod nazivom <code>data.txt</code> koji sadrži sledeće:</p>\n<pre>\n29,97,32,100,45\n15,88,5,75,22\n</pre>\n<p>Koji kod bi generisao sledeći red podataka?</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-py\">[29. 32. 45. 15.  5. 22.]\n</code></pre>",
      "answers": [
        {
          "answer": "<pre><code class=\"language-py\">filedata = np.genfromtxt('data.txt', delimiter=',')\noutput = np.any(filedata &#x3C; 50)\n\nprint(output)\n</code></pre>",
          "feedback": null,
          "audioId": null
        },
        {
          "answer": "<pre><code class=\"language-py\">filedata = np.genfromtxt('data.txt', delimiter=',')\noutput = np.all(filedata &#x3C; 50, axis=1)\n\nprint(output)\n</code></pre>",
          "feedback": null,
          "audioId": null
        },
        {
          "answer": "<pre><code class=\"language-py\">filedata = np.genfromtxt('data.txt', delimiter=',')\noutput = filedata[filedata &#x3C; 50]\n\nprint(output)\n</code></pre>",
